Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second L, as well as the one I suspect to be Kira, is... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second L, as well as the one I suspect to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. This is Takada Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Messages from Kira will now be transmitted as the law to the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can use Takada Kiyomi in this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.57,0:00:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove all bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.01,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(363,359)}Ridicule
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pieces are now in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this stage, {\alpha&HFF&}I should go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this stage, I should go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Lester.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come back to New York one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will support you from New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why do you want me back in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never boarded a plane alone in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to escort me to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. We managed to get into Yoshida Productions and NHN.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa's infiltration was a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, getting into NHN is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this, they won't suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As her manager, Mogi-san will be able to get in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely want someone to be able to go in and out freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll be watching Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near. {\alpha&HFF&}Let me speak to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near. Let me speak to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. {\alpha&HFF&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to capture Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I have come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to capture Kira, I have come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan? {\alpha&HFF&}Why did he tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan? Why did he tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L. {\alpha&HFF&}You should be watching Takada-san to aid your investigation on Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L. You should be watching Takada-san to aid your investigation on Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}I am currently in contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am currently in contact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to catch Kira, keeping an eye on NHN and Takada Kiyomi is common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please inform Takada that some members from the SPK has come to Japan to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bait for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I would like her to know this as well;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The SPK has only four members, myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will certainly try to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}we will get him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we will get him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Get him instead", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we are pretty close to each other. {\alpha&HFF&}We could even meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we are pretty close to each other. We could even meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, I'll count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the time we settle this Kira matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, since that time, this has been a one-on-one fight with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of going against L, I am going against L's successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going for it, I am going for it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet, we'll see who is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is at the higher position...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, this fight will come to an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will stand on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's revise what we have so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}We'll call him L-Kira for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is Kira. We'll call him L-Kira for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, {\alpha&HFF&}the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, {\alpha&HFF&}X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the other, the one who is holding the notebook, and doing the killing, X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira is doing the judgments, {\alpha&HFF&}and definitely has the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira is doing the judgments, and definitely has the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, L-Kira and X-Kira are using Takada as a bridge to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the actual method to beat Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}there are two ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the actual method to beat Kira, there are two ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first way will be to... {\alpha&HFF&}kill both L-Kira and X-Kira, and take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first way will be to... kill both L-Kira and X-Kira, and take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}we will never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we will never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way we work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing someone to see if the judgments will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of trial and error is not L's, nor my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L would not accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be meaningless as the successor to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I heard on the news that you're receiving countless fan letters daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It seems there are at least 200 of them each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200 of them? I'm getting jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listening to them without any pictures is pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think fan letters are something you should just skip through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read the messages from now on in a calm manner so that people listening to this won't notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the SPK on the move, {\alpha&HFF&}right now, for your own safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the SPK on the move, right now, for your own safety,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of just waiting for his messages, {\alpha&HFF&}you should go and tell him about your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of just waiting for his messages, you should go and tell him about your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light is making his move right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should not be just the spokesperson for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try to call out Kira from your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T has other missions: {\alpha&HFF&}creating a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T has other missions: creating a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to have you carrying out the judgment of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, so I'm sure you can do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that, information that you don't want the SPK to know can be passed on to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Light-kun for you! He's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. {\alpha&HFF&}Eliminate. Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. Eliminate. {\alpha&HFF&}Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate. Eliminate. Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send a fan letter that only I will recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, {\alpha&HFF&}include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, include five pages from the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I receive it, carry on with your judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not use the real notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}but carry out your judgments with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not use the real notebook, but carry out your judgments with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a fake one that looks like the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And use that for your judgments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have received the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... {\alpha&HFF&}what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is no need for me to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will just carry out God's will.
Comment: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this program?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the program that replaced "Kira's Realm".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up with something like this is just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Today's Miss Takada, we will introduce the four bodyguards of Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the 22nd World Female Karate Championships, Oyama Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former CIA investigator, Hal Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:09:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a SPK member among them, this Hal Lidner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Near didn't make any effort to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.63,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Shinjuku business district, six people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to choose X-Kira, who would I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:22.91,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's existence, as well as Kira's teachings, are to be considered good, and should be infused into the minds of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada was chosen because she is a supporter of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira must have known that she is a supporter of Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}A person that has a certain relationship with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira must have known that she is a supporter of Kira. A person that has a certain relationship with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not allow any criminal acts, no matter how small they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, targets for his judgments will include all the humans in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely want to hear Kira's voice and thoughts one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Kira's teaching is the straightest path to world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young people with talent should not be allowed to waste them. They should use their talents to improve society.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have instructions or directions from Kira, I think it's necessary for us to make our own judgments based on Kira's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Kira is Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is making sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ask, why am I not the main attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they said I'm the highlight of this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, highlight is highlight. The main attraction is something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, you have to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot. She doesn't know she's just being used by Light in his investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! If you go on, you might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. That's why I am saying this softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}She smirked at me! Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She smirked at me! {\alpha&HFF&}Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! She smirked at me! Misa is going to break her legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! {\alpha&HFF&}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?"... I was just going to ask the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner. She is my important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Takada-sama. I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... {\alpha&HFF&}Misa-Misa! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Misa-Misa! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi... Misa-Misa! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}if mister Aizawa is there, is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if mister Aizawa is there, {\alpha&HFF&}is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, if mister Aizawa is there, is it possible for me to speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is Aizawa. {\alpha&HFF&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is Aizawa. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When L meets Takada, {\alpha&HFF&}are there cameras and bugs used to record their conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When L meets Takada, are there cameras and bugs used to record their conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}Right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Right now, only bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they only use bugs, it's possible that X-Kira and L-Kira are communicating through Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means, Lidner is in a pretty dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put things bluntly, the most important thing right now is to let L focus on Takada and Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have to use this chance to get Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Gevanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's amazingly simple to trail him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not hiding or anything, and he has lived in the same room for four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he seems to be leading a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing his prosecution job normally as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he is X-Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is an extremely high possibility that Mikami is X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pay more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch him carefully until he goes back to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... don't make me do this again and again, NHN...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was only told "Please pay attention to what you say" again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will ask her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa, Takada wanted to have dinner with you and talk girl-to-girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kiyomi... what is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:14:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that be great? The show's host and highlight having dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama, the dinner is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's something I'm looking forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner, make sure we get a respectable room, and sit in with us for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san. Sorry for making you come at this late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really leave until I'm done with News 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Misa is actually quite fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?"? I really don't know how to answer your sudden question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be very busy these days. Do you manage to see him nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm seeing him. He's still just like a boy in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every night when he comes home, he's very sticky to me. It's very troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would like to let you know something in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to announce my engagement with him at the New Year Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You can't possibly get engaged with just one person consenting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a month since we agreed on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be okay for me to announce that in the show, host?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it can be done that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to use your authority as the host to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could you possibly... {\alpha&HFF&}try to get Kira to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could you possibly... try to get Kira to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira decides who he wants to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Kira decides who he wants to judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you as a friend. {\alpha&HFF&}Please don't say something as cold as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you as a friend. Please don't say something as cold as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter how bad a person it is, I don't kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine. Although I like Kira, he's soon going to be caught by Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's caught, you'll get your share too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will definitely be... {\alpha&HFF&}put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will definitely be... put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-sama! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will be with me, as the goddess of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Neither am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can have dinner when you are a bit older and have more manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, I'm older than you, Kiyomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to leave a table before the dinner ends, that's even worse manners, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochii!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an easy victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In tonight's meeting between Takada and Amane, their conversation was about "him".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, who is the real girlfriend of Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this, what I can say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light has Takada and Amane in a love triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, please be more serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not trying to make light of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not be easy for him to betray either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they will follow him with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, girl? You are inviting me to do that by wearing such short skirts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami took out a notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's writing something on it. {\alpha&HFF&}Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's writing something on it. Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami is getting off the train.
